{
  "stem": "7358.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a strong log cabin with a door.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And during the night, wolves and coyotes would come, and they would scratch all night on the door, because they became brazen, you know, because there was no one to fight them off, and they could-- I guess they knew there was a living person in that place.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they-- it was very frightening to be there alone, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I saw that they weren't able to break the door, so I sort of got used to the fact that they-- that this is every night they come, and they scratch the door.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They want to break into the log cabin that I was being housed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there's nothing I could do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was- they left me enough wood to feed the fire.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I was warm, and there was a little bit of food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I just waited to die there or whatever.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "God knows what I was thinking at the time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And one day, a farmer came looking for wood.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say-- it's hard for me to remember now, but I think I would say at least 10 days.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So after a few days, the farmer was coming to the forest to look for wood, and he realized that there were maybe four or five log cabins like that.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He realized, I guess, that they were abandoned.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So instead of chopping down wood from the trees, it was simpler to dismantle something like that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I could hear some noise from a distance hammering, and then he noticed that from my cabin, smoke was coming out through that little metal chimney.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he came, and there was a little window on top for light that they built.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
